OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FRiccardo Ehrman: Journalist
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fwho prompted Berlin Wall to
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Ffall dies                  
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Italian journalist Riccardo Ehrman, who
OL,6, will always be remembered for asking   
OL,7, the decisive question that led to      
OL,8, communist East Germany opening up the  
OL,9, Berlin Wall, has died aged 92.         
OL,11,FIt was Ehrman who in 1989 prompted     
OL,12,Fgovernment spokesman Gunter Schabowski 
OL,13,Fto explain that private travel would be
OL,14,Fallowed outside East Germany.          
OL,16,FAnd when pressed on when that would    
OL,17,Fhappen, Schabowski eventually announced
OL,18,F"right now, immediately".              
OL,20,FWithin hours the wall came down.       
